    dc:description "FIGURE 20. Sampling sites with records of Epeorus (Caucasiron) turcicus sp. nov. (locality numbers correspond to those given in parentheses in the list of material studied, arrow points to the area depicted on the larger map)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2625134/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2625122>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–5. Epeorus (Caucasiron) turcicus sp. nov., mature larvae (holotype [female] and paratype [male]): 1, habitus, dorsal; 2, habitus, ventral; 3, habitus, lateral; 4, head of male, dorsal; 5, head of female, dorsal." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2625122/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2625124>
    dc:description "FIGURES 6–8. Epeorus (Caucasiron) turcicus sp. nov., mature larvae: 6, labrum (a) ventral, (b) dorsal); 7, incisors of right mandible, ventral; 8, incisors of left mandible, ventral." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2625124/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2625126>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9–10. Epeorus (Caucasiron) turcicus sp. nov., mature larvae: 9, middle leg, dorsal; 10, setae on dorsal surface of femora." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2625126/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2625130>
    dc:description "FIGURES 11–18. Epeorus (Caucasiron) turcicus sp. nov., mature larvae: 11, abdominal tergum VII, surface and posterior margin; 12, gill I; 13, gill III; 14, gill VII (flattened on the slide); 15a–c, gill plates VII (in natural position from ventral view), variability in shape; 16, gill plates VII, ventral view; 17, sternum IX, male; 18, sternum IX, female." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2625130/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2625132>
    dc:description "FIGURE 19. Bayesian maximum credibility COI gene tree of the subgenus Caucasiron with results of individual species" ;
